code: @Override public T onDataSet(DataSet ds, Object... payloads) {     if (payloads.length != payloadTypes.length) {         String message = format("Received %d payloads, but expected %d.", payloads.length, payloadTypes.length).         throw new IllegalArgumentException(message).     }     for (int i = 0. i < payloads.length. i++) {         payloads[i] = camelContext.getTypeConverter().convertTo(payloadTypes[i], payloads[i]).     }     return doOnDataSet(ds, payloads). }
public abstract T doOnDataSet(DataSet ds, Object... payloads).
